description:
Animal's Super Senses - Episode 5: Superhuman Senses | Wildlife Documentary

Watch 'Animal's Super Senses - Episode 6' here: https://youtu.be/Boh1QzB_ayc

There are senses we share with most animals, but what about those senses that humans are equipped with? Infrared light, electromagnetic waves, and ultrasound are all found within a spectrum of sensory information that just passes by ordinary humans. This episode is all about those superhuman senses  animal sensory systems that can detect magnetic fields (magneto-reception), electric fields (electroreception), and infrared radiation.
